Title: The Spirit and Body of Shen-zin Su
Description:
Well, that wraps it up here, doesn't it $n?  Now that we've got these two roused and all friendly towards you, we just need to get them back to the Temple of Five Dawns.

You go ahead. I'm going to say my goodbyes, then I'll follow you up shortly.
ObjectivesText: Bring Shu and Wugou, the spirits of water and earth, to the Temple of Five Dawns.  A cart is waiting near the road to take you there.
